1445  {
1446  }

1450  }

1452  template <class ClosureDataType>
1453  class ClosureHandler : public DepthSense::GenericFunctionHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, void (*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property, ClosureDataType closureData)>
1454  {
1455  public:
1456  ClosureHandler (typename DepthSense::GenericFunctionHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, void (*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property, ClosureDataType closureData)>::Function closure, ClosureDataType closureData)
1457  : DepthSense::GenericFunctionHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, void (*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property, ClosureDataType closureData)>(closure), _closureData(closureData)
1458  {
1459  }
1460  virtual void operator () (DepthSense::Interface obj, PropertyChangedData data)
1461  {
1462  _func(obj, data.property, _closureData);
1463  }
1464  private:
1465  ClosureDataType _closureData;
1466  };
1467  template <class ObjectType>
1468  class MethodHandler : public DepthSense::GenericMethodHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, ObjectType, void (ObjectType::*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property)>
1469  {
1470  public:
1471  MethodHandler (ObjectType* obj, typename DepthSense::GenericMethodHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, ObjectType, void (ObjectType::*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property)>::Method method)
1472  : DepthSense::GenericMethodHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, ObjectType, void (ObjectType::*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property)>(obj, method)
1473  {
1474  }
1475  virtual void operator () (DepthSense::Interface obj, PropertyChangedData data)
1476  {
1477  ((DepthSense::GenericMethodHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, ObjectType, void (ObjectType::*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property)>::_obj)->*(DepthSense::GenericMethodHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, ObjectType, void (ObjectType::*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property)>::_method))(obj, data.property);
1478  }
1479  };
1480  #endif
1481  public:
